The EFF has confirmed their leader Julius Malema will be speaking at their final rally despite suffering a personal loss this weekend. Courtesy #DStv403 • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - EFF leader Julius Malema will be speaking at their final rally despite suffering a personal loss this weekend. The party sent its condolences to the Malema family. READ: Malema's grandmother dies Malema's grandmother Sarah Malema died on Saturday morning. The EFF stated Malema would still address the Tshela Thupa rally on Sunday at the Orlando Stadium in Soweto.